metadata.name: Stream Tide Planet
metadata.description:
Stream Tide is an open-source patronage tool designed to amplify financial support through donation matching from the community grant pool. 

Turning a small stream of support into a tidal wave of support.

Stream Tide is dedicated to supporting and empowering creative artists and culture builders by providing a comprehensive infrastructure for funding their work. We believe that financial support is crucial for the success and growth of these individuals and organizations, and we aim to play a role in facilitating positive change in the industry through grant programs and innovative Web3 solutions. 

We're heavily inspired by Plural Funding and Quadratic Funding concepts.

Our vision is to create a world where creative talents and cultural pioneers have the resources they need to realize their potential and make their mark. We strive to be a driving force behind the growth of the creative arts and culture building, enabling everyone to pursue their passions and bring their ideas to life and redefine the meaning of work by leveraging Web3 technology.

https://streamtide.io/
